results.name: G.f.: Sum_{k>=1} (-1)^(k + 1) * k * x^(k^2) / (1 - x^k).
comment: Excess of sum of odd divisors of n that are <= sqrt(n) over sum of even divisors of n that are <= sqrt(n).
mathematica: nmax = 80; CoefficientList[Series[Sum[(-1)^(k + 1) k x^(k^2)/(1 - x^k), {k, 1, nmax}], {x, 0, nmax}], x] // Rest
program: (PARI) a(n) = sumdiv(n, d, if (d^2<=n, if (d%2, d, -d))); \\ _Michel Marcus_, Apr 05 2020
results.author: _Ilya Gutkovskiy_, Apr 05 2020
